               <head>Bigde Shesh by Shelomoh Shemama ben Shmu'el</head>
					
               
               
               
               <msContents rend="visible">
						
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>Bigde Shesh by Shelomoh Shemama ben Shmu'el, novellae on the
                            Shulḥan arukh, Ḥoshen mishpaṭ</summary>
						
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
						
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="visible">
							
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">בגדי שש: חדושים על שולחן ערוך</title>
							
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Bigde shesh: ḥidushim 'al Shulḥan
                                arukh</title>
							
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
								
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Last volume of a 17-volume set.</p>
								
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Rest of the volumes: Or
                                    10064-10067 (Gaster 623-626): On Shulḥan Arukh, Orah Ḥayim.
                                    Sefer Migeba'ot Shesh; Or 10068-10070 (Gaster 620-622): about
                                    Yoreh De'ah; Or 10071-10079 (Gaster 610-619): on Ḥoshen
                                    mishpaṭ.</p>
								
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The manuscript contains homiletic commentaries,
                                    extracts from the Author’s books Kutonet Shesh and Amude Shesh,
                                    responsa and lists of the author’s family members from between
                                    the years תק"ץ-תר"ד (from 1739 to
                                1843).</p>
								
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Autograph?</p>
							
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
							
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="367v"/>
						
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
					
               
               
               
               </msContents>
					
               
               
               
